#: src/Plugin.php:315
msgid "ActiveLayer automatically protects form submissions on this site after an API key is connected. When a form is submitted, ActiveLayer sends submission details (such as names, email addresses, form field values, IP addresses, and user agent strings) to the ActiveLayer API for spam analysis. This data is used exclusively to determine whether a submission is spam and may be stored temporarily in accordance with the ActiveLayer Privacy Policy. Site administrators can disable protection for individual forms in the ActiveLayer integration settings if needed."
msgstr ""

